2. The children to be displayed inside Column were wrapped in `Expanded` which again takes up default space for its child. Here, instead of `Expanded`, use `Flexible` which takes the space as applicable to its child.

3. The Container used to display the data from `future builder` again expands to the entire screen if not provided a `height`. So just provide a custom `height` to the Container.

